'''''Bairagirchar High School''''' is a secondary school in [[Katiadi Upazila]], [[Kishoreganj District]], [[Dhaka Division]], [[Bangladesh]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.moedu.gov.bd/index.php?option=com_docman&task=doc_download&gid=4300&Itemid= |title=List of Institutions |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |website=Ministry of Education |format=XLS |accessdate=July 15, 2014}}</ref>
== History == Bairagirchar High School is one of the oldest schools in Katiadi, Kishoregonj. The school was established after the liberation war of Bangladesh. In 1972 some renowned people of Bairagirchat planned to set up a school in the village so they took initiative for the establishment of the school. <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dhakaeducationboard.gov.bd/institution/admin |title=Archived copy |access-date=2015-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150612135414/http://www.dhakaeducationboard.gov.bd/institution/admin |archive-date=2015-06-12 |dead-url=yes |df= }}</ref>
